name: FOODPRINT
0:
”Alexa, launch food print”
”Alexa, ask food print to get the foodprint for beef and lamb”
”Alexa, open food print for the foodprint of romaine lettuce”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food print
des: The production of food is a major source of greenhouse gas emissions. However, certain food emits significantly more carbon than some others such as beef and lamb. Use FOODPRINT to learn more about the environmental footprint your food has. FOODPRINT supports over 200 different types of food. Please note, you cannot ask about the carbon emission of sandwhich. Instead, you can ask about bread, ham, lettuce, and tomatoes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
